{"tid":1126460,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓與鸚鵡可否共存？","createTime":"2019-04-26T11:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T13:42:32.000Z","uid":7304,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fa7eb8a81442e559127335969fb6be074ed2fcc9","tid":1126460,"uid":7304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"本身已養三貓，一隻五歲，兩隻三歲幾！<br />\n<br />\n兩隻都幾純，一隻就百厭小小～<br />\n<br />\n依大半年黎不斷接觸鸚鵡覺得佢地超級可愛！<br />\n<br />\n所以想用心用力照顧佢地一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網睇到有啲人就話冇乜野仲好fd<br />\n<br />\n有啲人就話可能會有危險&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n心目中係想養凱克，知道佢係比較曳好貪玩<br />\n<br />\n唔知可唔可以夾到屋企啲貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有經驗可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5f5fb164ca11b913ffd395c673073e18f1bd00","tid":1126460,"uid":120980,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:48:18.000Z","msg":"事實上<br />\n你真係要做實驗將佢地拍埋一齊先知佢地共唔共存到<br />\n呢樣嘢真係話唔埋<br />\n人地啲例子得<br />\n都代表唔到你得"},{"pid":"1f5c39f7bc3d87b3016e4d435272f8d447a45650","tid":1126460,"uid":176231,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"屋企有養兩隻貓 一隻鸚鵡 <br />\n前兩日隻貓先摑左隻雀一把<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658df30db46fee1f3d8cb3960dc077b963060512","tid":1126460,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"1f5c39f7bc3d87b3016e4d435272f8d447a45650","tid":1126460,"uid":176231,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"屋企有養兩隻貓 一隻鸚鵡 <br />\n前兩日隻貓先摑左隻雀一把<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"應該仲會推隻雀跳樓<img src=\"/assets/face